00:03:09,300 --> 00:03:11,530
Longxuan dan aku
akan berkultivasi sebentar.

14
00:03:11,530 --> 00:03:12,950
Jaga di luar

15
00:03:12,950 --> 00:03:14,180
dan jangan pergi

16
